'''''En Purushanthaan Enakku Mattumthaan''''' is a [[Tamil films of 1989|1989]] [[Cinema of India|Indian]] [[Tamil language|Tamil]] film,  directed by  [[Manobala]] and produced by V. M. J. Manivannan. The film stars [[Vijayakanth]], [[Suhasini Mani Ratnam]] and [[Rekha (South Indian actress)|Rekha]] in lead roles. The film had musical score by [[Ilayaraja]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://entertainment.oneindia.in/tamil/movies/en-purushanthaan-enakku-mattumthaan.html|title=En Purushanthaan Enakku Mattumthaan|accessdate=2014-08-11|publisher=entertainment.oneindia.in}}</ref> The film was remade in Hindi as ''[[Mera Pati Sirf Mera Hai]]'' starring [[Jeetendra]]. Manobala also directed the Hindi version.

==Cast==
*[[Vijayakanth]] as Marudhu
*[[Suhasini Mani Ratnam]]
*[[Rekha (South Indian actress)|Rekha]] as Saradha

==Soundtrack==
The music was composed by [[Ilaiyaraaja]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.raaga.com/channels/tamil/moviedetail.asp?mid=t0002683|title=En Purushan Thaan Enakku Mattum Thaan Songs|accessdate=2014-08-11|publisher=raaga.com}}</ref>

